      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s seriously in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
