    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, maintained to exacting factory specifications. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, paired with a precision-shifting 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically, this unit is beyond reproach: the critical VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis is rock-solid with zero subframe fatigue, and the suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings for razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the aesthetic condition is commensurate with its mechanical excellence. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless exterior. Interior like new. Full service history. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
