    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade example, maintained with obsessive attention to detail since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, sporting a deep, mirror-like shine thanks to a professional ceramic coating and a life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats retain their original matte finish and firm bolsters, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Every button, switch, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is truly indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48900.0,
